    <bodyText>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>We will verify income on every application. Income must be paid and contracted in GBP (£) and be subject to UK tax and National Insurance contributions.</p>
<p><strong>For new clients</strong></p>
<p>For repayment mortgages a minimum household income of £20,000 per annum is required.</p>
<p>Interest only or part and part is only available where 1 applicant earns in excess of £50,000 per annum or joint income exceeds £75,000 per annum (where neither applicant fulfils the individual income requirement of £50,000).</p>
<p><strong>For existing customers moving home</strong></p>
<p>For porting and moving applications a minimum household income of £20,000 per annum is required. Exceptions may be considered for existing customers who do not require additional borrowing.</p>
<p>Additional borrowing on interest only is only available where 1 applicant earns in excess of £50,000 per annum or joint income exceeds £75,000 per annum (where neither applicant fulfils the individual income requirement of £50,000).</p>
<p><strong>The following is applicable to both new and existing customers:</strong></p>]]></Value>
